Name: Legacy ID
Description: Identifier type to record optional previous identifers

Name: SSN
Format description: Identifier should be 1 letter, followed by a dash and 7 numerical characters. Eg, A-0010902

Name: ART Unique Number
Description: Unique ART number for patients on ART
Format description: Should be 3 digits then digit 0 or 1 lastly 8 digits. E.g. (333033333333)
